snippet.title: ☵ HIRAETH #game new #teaser for #Indiegogo pre-launch page (updated)
snippet.description:
Music: https://www.youtube.com/@UCPfKR3AG7uvJn8IvlXtP1VQ  , Voice Actor: https://www.youtube.com/@UCi5iDUWe7mGWc6d6tWSe9Dw 

Only on @indiegogo pre launch page you can claim your VANGUARD perk in price of SURVIVOR! 

Sign up for details https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/hiraeth-indie-game-sci-fi-survival-rich-story/coming_soon/

With VANGUARD perk you will have many rewards:
☵ HIRAETH game @Steam key
☵ HIRAETH game #Soundtrack key
Immortalized in ☵ HIRAETH: Memory Lane Polaroid
Immortalized in ☵ HIRAETH: name in colony databases and credits
Discord 'Hiraeth Backer' Role and TitleSteam Playtest and demo VIP access
and more!

All this for the price of the basic game!

Music composer: Michele Masin @michelemasincomposer https://www.imdb.com/name/nm13428058/ 
Voice Actor: Andy Mack @andymackvoice https://andymackvoice.com
@andymackvoice
